      <description>&lt;p&gt;
    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;/assets/images/default/summaryblog.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Summary Blog&#34; /&gt;
      
